Name: Access
Description: The summarized access levels that this user has
Options: Super Admin (super_admin); Contacts (contacts); Marketing (marketing); Sales (sales); Service (service); Reports (reports); Partner (partner_program_tools); Account (account); Partner Admin (partner_admin)

Name: Seat
Description: The seats assigned to this user

Name: Deactivated
Description: Users who are deactivated and no longer have access to this HubSpot account.

Name: Default Team (Formerly Main Team)
Description: The assigned primary team of the user

Name: Extra Teams
Description: The secondary teams for the user

Name: Calendar Status
Description: Personal calendar connected to use HubSpot Meetings, calendar sync and scheduling pages.

Name: Email Status
Description: Personal email accounts connected to HubSpot to log, track, send, and receive emails.

Name: Invite Status
Description: The user's invite status.
Options: Deactivated (deactivated) [READ-ONLY]; Invite pending (invite_pending) [READ-ONLY]; Invite bounced (invite_bounced) [READ-ONLY]; Invite accepted (invite_accepted) [READ-ONLY]

Name: Last Active
Description: The last time this user performed actions within the app on desktop or mobile. Updated daily.

Name: Last Password Change
Description: The last time this user updated their password.

Name: Scheduling Pages
Description: Shares personal availability in scheduling pages to allow prospects to book time on their connected calendar.

Name: Additional Phone
Description: The user's additional phone number

Name: Permission Sets
Description: The permission sets assigned to this user

Name: Calendar Sync
Description: Calendar sync logs new meetings from their primary calendar to existing contacts in HubSpot.

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user who created this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Created date
Description: The date and time at which this object was created. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Email
Description: The user's email address.

Name: Last Name
Description: The user's last or family name.

Name: First Name
Description: The user's first or given name.

Name: Internal User ID
Description: The user's unique internal ID in HubSpot's centralized database. This is not portal-specific.

Name: Invite Accepted Time
Description: The time the user accepted their invite to the portal.

Name: Partner
Description: Property to say if a user is working on that hub on behalf of a Solutions Partner or a Solutions Provider

Name: Job Title
Description: Displays the user's job title.

Name: Object last modified date/time
Description: Most recent timestamp of any property update for this object. This includes HubSpot internal properties, which can be visible or hidden. This property is updated automatically.

Name: Main Phone
Description: The user's main phone number

Name: Manager
Description: The user's manager. Can be any non-deactivated or non-partner user in the account

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record source detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source
Description: How this record was created.

Name: Partner User
Description: The type of partner user (partner or provider) if applicable

Name: SCIM Status
Description: Demonstrates whether the user is managed by SCIM
Options: Managed by SCIM (true); Not Managed by SCIM (false)

Name: Name
Description: The user's full name or  email. If first/last name do not exist, then the email will be given.

Description: Controls whether the user's hs_standard_time_zone property auto updates based on their browser location when using timezone enabled apps

Description: The user who last updated this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Description: The main team, extra team, and any child team assigned to the user.

Name: Owner assigned date
Description: The most recent timestamp of when an owner was assigned to this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Description: The owner of the object.

Description: The main team of the record owner. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.
